Metadata.Title: SHAMEFUL CONDUIT
Metadata.Description: Good Evening 47,IAGO is conducting an information auction under the pretext of a fashion show. High level partners are involved in it who wants their secrets to remain secrets and not become pressure points for blackmail. They have requested the ICA to handle their problem and make sure none of the auction participants live to tell the tale. It has been requested to mask the deaths as "accidents" to prevent any investigations.Goodluck 47.
